title: Fem Van Empel Puts on Masterclass in Storm-Delayed European Championships
content:
The 21-year-old took the lead on the opening lap and blasted her way to victory, leading home a Dutch 1-2 with Ceylin del Carmen Alvarado.

Read the full article at Fem Van Empel Puts on Masterclass in Storm-Delayed European Championships on Velo.
author: sadhbhoshea
